HEADWORD: Conceitless
<hw>Con*ceit"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without wit; stupid.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Think'st thou I am so shallow, so <qex>conceitless</qex>.⟦br⟧
To be seduced by thy flattery?</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Conceivable</ent>⟦br⟧
